metadata.name: Mysterious Stars Valley
metadata.description:
This is one of my favorite photos because I got my first photography award with this photo from Qeshm World Geopark Management Cultural Heritage, Tourism and Handicrafts of Qeshm Free Zone Organization, in Iran.
Stars Valley is one of the most mysterious places in Qeshm Island, Iran. The locals believe that ghosts roam in this valley at night and they hear the sound of ghosts.
Do not go to this valley at night!!
